              <span class="icon-bar"></span>
              <span class="icon-bar"></span>
              <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            </button>
            <a href="/" class="navbar-brand">Home</a>
          </div>
          <nav  role="navigation">
            <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
             <%for(i=0;i<nav.length;i++){%>
              <li>
                <a href="<%=nav[i].link%>"><%=nav[i].name%></a>
              </li>
            <%}%>
            </ul>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </header>
      <div class="row">
    <h1 id="heads">Library</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    
    <div class="col-md-12">
    <h3 id="quote">"Books are the quietest and most constant of friends; they are the most accessible and wisest of counselors, and the most patient of teachers."
      ― Charles W. Eliot</h3>
      </div>
     
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
       <br>
       <br>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="members">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
      <h2 id="heads1">What our members say!</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
     <div class="row">
       <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card" style="width: 30rem;">
          <div class="card-body" style="margin-left: 15%; text-align: justify;">
            <p class="card-text">"Listen up, the library is cool and we all secretly know it. But what's even cooler is that this app lets you borrow e-books, audiobooks, music, and more for free."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
       <div class="card" style="width: 30rem;">
         <div class="card-body" style="margin-left: 15%; text-align: justify;">
           <p class="card-text">"This app give access to multiple contents with a potentially infinite number of resources and selections at hand. We can access an enormous amount of knowledge, facilitating the expansion of education. "</p>
         </div>
       </div>
   </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="card" style="width: 30rem;">
        <div class="card-body" style="margin-left: 10%; text-align: justify;">
          <p class="card-text">"Put your local library in your pocket with this app, an ebook- and audiobook-borrowing app with a wealth of literary offerings available on demand."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div> 
  </div>
  <!-- Books -->
  <div id="booksdetail">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
   <h2>You will find</h2>
    </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class=col-md-12 style="text-align: center;">
  <div class="slideshow-container">

    <!-- Full-width images with number and caption text -->
    <div class="mySlides fade">
      <div class="numbertext">1 / 3</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: cursive;">Entertainment</h3>
      <img src="images/inmjeeves.jpg" style="width:30%; height: 400px;">
      <img src="images/midnightside.jpg" style="width:30%; height:400px;">
      <img src="images/memmidnight.jpg" style="width:30%; height:400px;">
      <div class="text">Caption Text</div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="mySlides fade">
      <div class="numbertext">2 / 3</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: cursive;">Education</h3>
      <img src="images/javascriptbook.jpg" style="width:30%; height:400px;">
      <img src="images/expressjsbook.jpg" style="width:30%; height: 400px;">
      <img src="images/nodejsbook.jpg" style="width:30%; height:400px;">
      <div class="text">Caption Two</div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="mySlides fade">
      <div class="numbertext">3 / 3</div>
      <h3 style="font-family: cursive;">Kids Learning</h3>
      <img src="images/tinklesup.jpg" style="width:30%; height:400px;">
      <img src="images/chefs.jpg" style="width:30%; height:420px;">
      <img src="images/balarama.jpg" style="width:30%; height:400px;">
      <div class="text">Caption Three</div>
    </div>
  
    <!-- Next and previous buttons -->
    <a class="prev" onclick="plusSlides(-1)">&#10094;</a>
    <a class="next" onclick="plusSlides(1)">&#10095;</a>
  </div>
  <br>
  
  <!-- The dots/circles -->
  <div style="text-align:center">
    <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(1)"></span>
    <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(2)"></span>
    <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(3)"></span>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

